<br>
Atm I have run3, stam3, durability3, fury2 and healing gift1, my next points will go to Agility, Holy Steed and Improved Lay Hands. Then I will prolly do Physical Enhancement and some mental clarity.. havent decided yet.<br>
<br>
Im a HP freak though ...to each his own...have fun with it ther is no *right* way to do it.  <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=4342 target="_blank"><img src=http://www.prowlerz.net/alarie/hyp20.jpg border=0></a>
