<br>
I initially went the route you are proposing and put 3 points into wisdom and 3 into natural regen. I don't regret these choices. However, eventually I had to go back and put 3 into run speed. It really makes a big difference all the time whether you are pulling for an AE group, running for the zoneline with some baddies in tow, or doing CR before you get holy steed. I would suggest you get all three if wisdom is important to you.  <p><table border="0" width="41%">
